videos.description: Zia Cooke runs the break and uses a spin move to confuse her defender and pull up to hit the transition bucket for South Carolina.

videos.description: Aliyah Boston gets inside and fights off defenders to get the ball up and in through contact for an and-1 basket for South Carolina.

videos.description: Aliyah Boston puts on a stellar defensive performance as she records five blocks in South Carolina's season-opening win on the road against NC State.
